{
  "id": "godot4_input_map_four_actions",
  "app": "godot4",
  "task": "Edit /home/user/godot_projects/rpg_game/project.godot. The [input] section already defines move_left (A) and move_right (D). Preserve those entries and add four new input actions inside the same [input] section: move_up bound to W, move_down bound to S, attack bound to J, and interact bound to E. For every new action use the same dictionary format as the existing move_left entry (deadzone=0.5 and a single InputEventKey event with the physical_keycode set to the ASCII uppercase code of the letter — W=87, S=83, J=74, E=69). Save the file.",
  "env": {
